

Pre-requisites
a. Working installation of pentaho biserver-ce-3.8.0-stable

JNDI Configuration - Pentaho Data Integration
* Edit the $PDI_HOME/simple-jndi/jdbc.properties file and append the contents of the fragment in configuration fragments folder. Modify as necessary. 


JNDI configuration - Pentaho BI 
* Edit the $PENTAHO_BI_HOME/tomcat/webapps/WEB-INF/web.xml and add the content of configuration fragment 'web.xml-fragment' in the appropriate location. Modify the property values as necessary. 

* Edit the $PENTAHO_BI_HOME/tomcat/conf/context.xml and add the content of the configuration fragment 'context.xml-fragment' at the end of the file.Modify the propery values as necessary. 

To install the MoTeCH Business Intelligence system
1. Run motech_dw.sql to create the database for the data warehouse
2. Copy/symlink motech-bi-solution to the pentaho solutions directory
